今年我们决定打破传统，外出度圣诞节。
We decided to break with tradition this year and go away for Christmas.

如果一座城市拆除它原有的历史建筑而不是去保护它们，这座城市可能会变得没有特色，而且它对游客的吸引力会降低。
If a city demolished its historical buildings instead of preserving them, 
it would become characterless and less appealing to tourists.

随着英语在全球的普及，很多小语种濒临灭绝，据估计每两周就有一门语言消失。
With the popularization of English worldwide, 
many minority languages are on the verge of extinction and it is estimated that one language dies out every two weeks.

今天，深圳、广州和其他的中国大都市里到处充斥着公寓楼、高层办公大楼以及巨型购物中心。
这些建筑物尽管可以为居民和职员提供方便和现代化的舒适设施，但他们通常看起来很平庸，缺乏艺术价值。
Today, Shenzhen, Guangzhou and other Chinese metropolises are filled with apartment complexes, 
office towers and mega-malls. These structures, despite offering convenience and modern comforts to residents and employees, 
tend to be visually plain and lacking in artistic value.  
